pan fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">6</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）因外伤眼影响健眼，对侧眼有发生交感性眼炎可能；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">7</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）因存在的其他器官损伤，增加手术难度，手术可能因此终止或推迟进行；可能诱发心脑血管意外或加重原有疾病；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">8</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）术中可能根据病情变化改变术式；</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">9</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">）除上述情况外，本医疗措施尚有可能发生的其他并发症或者需要提请患者及家属特别注意的其他事项，如___________________________________________　　　　　　　</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">4</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.我理解如果我患有高血压、心脏病、糖尿病、肝肾功能不全、静脉血栓等疾病或者有吸烟史，以上这些风险可能会加大，或者在术中或术后出现相关的病情加重或心脑血管意外，甚至死亡。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontbold="1" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">特殊风险或主要高危因素</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">我理解根据我个人的病情，我可能出现以下特殊并发症或风险：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><input name="新增的输入域" operatercreater="0" border-style="1" forecolor="#000000"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">                                                                </span></input><p operatercreater="0" /><span forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0"> 一旦发生上述风险和意外，医生会采取积极应对措施。</span><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row><row id="C1C6ACBB1056" width="660" operatercreater="0"><cell id="C1C6ACBB1057" width="660" operatercreater="0"><span fontbold="1" forecolor="#000000" operatercreater="0">患者知情选择</span><p operatercreater="0" /><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\1.png" type="" saveinfile="1" operatercreater="0">iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAwAAAAKCAIAAAAPTiitAAAAAXNSR0IArs4